animeTitle: Protagonist System: I Become a Big Shot in Every World
otherNames: Protagonist System: I Become a Big Shot in Every World, 主角系统：我在各界当大佬
synopsis: Qin Chuan, an ordinary man, accidentally transmigrates to the world of Da Zhou, becoming the number one rich playboy. Everyone laughs at me, thinking I'm a useless waste, only to be shocked and kneel before me when they see my luxury car. Even the Empress bows down before my famous vehicle... I originally intended to continue dominating Da Zhou, but the system pushes me to conquer countless worlds and become the ultimate protagonist in a power fantasy?!
